==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nuclear power
<hw>nuclear power</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Power derived from
nuclear reactions; -- used at present especially of electrical power
generated in atomic reactors, but encompassing also fusion
power.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> atomic energy, atomic power, nuclear energy, nuclear
energy.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A country possessing nuclear weapons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nuclear-powered ship</ent>⟦br⟧
